reviewText: Loved the content and practical articles and tools!! I learned ways to increased my effectiveness as a leader of change. I would have liked more accountability and/or feedback on the worksheets or use of the LMS to provide walk through for filling out the worksheets and planning docs.
Interesting presentation, impactful content and easy to comprehend. Keeps the listeners and readers engaged.
A​bsolutely amazing material and structure working to implement the framework for a longterm research product at my current employer with extensive documentation for completion.
